p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Again, though, nobody agrees with me, and the S=
EC wants to ban, you know, the stuff I am talking about. If that sounds vag=
ue, it is. The SEC has proposed a new rule, Rule 9j-1, banning manipulation=
 of securities-based swaps. Part of this =E2=80=94=C2=A0Rule 9j-1(a) =E2=80=
=94=C2=A0basically bans market manipulation and insider trading in CDS; the=
 SEC originally proposed this in 2010 and is coming back to it now.[2] But =
Rule 9j-1(b) is intended to ban CDS shenanigans. From <a href=3D"https://li=
